  Other - sorry for the ugliness and frustration you are about
  to experience.<br/>
  </div>
</td><td class='paneSidebar'>
  <div class='pvar-sidebar sidebar'>
    <%= render :partial => "welcome/sidebar", :locals => { :menuId => menuId } %>
